    "description": {
      "value": "<p>(To cast this jutsu, the target must be airborne) You fuel your weapon with sapping chakra, then leap into the air and strike your opponent in their abdomen. Make a melee Taijutsu attack against an airborne target. On hit they take your [weapons damage] +5d8. A creature hit by this jutsu also takes double fall damage as they are sent plummeting into the ground. If you reduce a creatures to 0 hit points with this jutsu, regain health equal to the amount of damage dealt with this jutsu.</p><p>If this jutsu is cast as a Chain 2, increase the damage die by +5, if this jutsu is cast as a Chain 3, increase the damage die by an additional +5</p>",
